## 🔥 All Files Are Already Implemented!

### Authentication APIs:
- ✅ POST `/api/auth/register` - Create new user
- ✅ POST `/api/auth/login` - Login user, get JWT token
- ✅ GET `/api/auth/me` - Get current authenticated user
- ✅ POST `/api/auth/logout` - Logout user

### Assessment APIs:
- ✅ POST `/api/analyze-relationship` - AI-powered relationship analysis
- ✅ GET `/api/assessments` - Get all assessments for user
- ✅ POST `/api/assessments` - Save new assessment
- ✅ GET `/api/assessments/[id]` - Get specific assessment

### Utility APIs:
- ✅ POST `/api/create-test-user` - Create test user

### Database:
- ✅ `src/lib/db.ts` - Prisma database client
- ✅ `prisma/schema.prisma` - Database schema

